qDef.qDef:
Sum({$<Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Competitor Share Volume])
 /
  Sum({$<Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Customer Volume])

COUNT(
{$< 
Year= {$(v_Max_Year)},
[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"},
Quarter=,
Month= ,
[Customer Key] = {'=sum({1<[Year]={$(v_Max_Year_LY)} >} [Invoice Amount USD])>0 and sum({1<[Year]={$(v_Max_Year)} >} [Invoice Amount USD]) >0'},
[Customer Purchase Behavior] ={'Tender Bid'}
>} DISTINCT [Customer Key])
Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT]) *1000
Sum({$<Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Customer Volume])

( Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])*1000 )
     
     /
( Sum({$<Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Customer Volume])
     )
Sum({$<Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Competitor Share Volume])

Sum({$<Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Competitor Share Volume])
 /
  Sum({$<Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Customer Volume])
